('40925DD66C3143bb88BBE7A1C7278FA7', 'level 2 driving automation', '3.7.39', '__driver support system__ that provides sustained lateral and longitudinal vehicle motion control within a specific __operational design domain__ with the expectation that a __conventional driver__ completes the object and event detection and response',
