('386BE5C5F5924b909CE60CCEC1EA437C', 'level 4 ADS', '3.7.312', '__ADS__ that is capable of operating within a specific __ODD__ and providing its own __fallback__, without any expectation that a human __driver__ will respond to a request to intervene',
