('30D0139B138E427995A7169B36C821FA', 'level 5 ADS', '3.7.313', '__ADS__ that is capable of unconditional (i.e., not __ODD__-specific) operation and providing its own __fallback__, without any expectation that a human __driver__ will respond to a request to intervene',
